Hey guys,
Here is my arrangement of the remix of "Tiny Little Adiantum" , from the album "TOHO BOSSA NOVA 2", a Touhou Project arrangement album in bossa nova style, called Omae Wa Mou. I made the drum track and piano in this video.

And as always, enjoy!

Please note: This visual format is for effect only and I would suggest using my Synthesia-only videos to try and learn the songs (only as an alternative to sheet music, which is much better than Synthesia), as the keys may not 100% line up with my piano.

Song: “Omae Wa Mou”
Artist: deadman 死人, Shibayan Records
Original track: "Tiny Little Adiantum" https://youtu.be/rB7XFQgJHBI
